overview: Kingdom hearts timeline is a series and a huge project of Everglow, a Kingdom Hearts youtuber. This series will tell you and help you to understand the lore of Kingdom Hearts. It is composed of all the Kingdom Hearts titles released so far, placed in chronogical order; which means that every single cutscene and/or gameplay part will follow the exact order of the events of the saga.
name: Kingdom Hearts Timeline

episodes.name: A Pure Heart Filled with Light
Destiny is Never Left to Chance
